To test the program, you should have mnist dataset in ./data/ directory. the program will download the dataset automatically.
The program is a simple demo of classification RBM testing on dataset minist.

Software Required:
python 2.7
numpy


How to run it?
python main.py

paper reference:
"A Practical Guide to Training Restricted Boltzmann Machines" Geoffrey Hinton
"An Introduction to Restricted Boltzmann Machines" Asja Fischer1,2 and Christian Igel2
"Learning Algorithms for the Classification Restricted Boltzmann Machine" Hugo Larochelle, Michael Mandel, Razvan Pascanu, Yoshua Bengio

